{"tid":1947484,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【全城禁聚】同一地點倘有兩組人聚集 距離不足1.5米亦屬違法","createTime":"2020-03-28T10:16:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T09:17:28.000Z","uid":13395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"10b2c306dc89c729ef3ef52071aab32255d1b818","tid":1947484,"uid":13395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T10:16:04.000Z","msg":"Source:<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2QNPD3y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2QNPD3y&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq9HbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=255bf3e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2QNPD3y</a>"},{"pid":"0e2a0384204bb2268974ea1596ac084b554b378d","tid":1947484,"uid":13395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T10:16:42.000Z","msg":"「禁聚令」將於明日凌晨開始，為期14日，食衞局指，當局可委任任何公職人員進行執法，可以有權驅散多於4人，而並非豁免場合下的聚集，或在公眾地方同一地點有兩組或以上人群聚集，而兩者距離不足1.5米及多於4人時，執法人員均有權可解散有關聚集，若不遵從命令則屬犯罪。<br />\n<br />\n食衞局副秘書長陳偉基指，雖同一戶人即使多於4人聚集可獲豁免，包括掃墓及其他活動，但若兩組人群一同聚集，而距離不足1.5米亦會被驅散。"},{"pid":"5d4778d16741ffe6a31c28a9a1b884e4704680a2","tid":1947484,"uid":318069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T10:19:03.000Z","msg":"可委任任何公職人員進行執法，可以有權驅散多於4人<br />\n<br />\n食環都有胡椒噴霧用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"181804f65b968f6dff91a0377dd1e868bb868546","tid":1947484,"uid":267801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:06:57.000Z","msg":"dklm 香港地有邊度唔使排隊，係唔係一排隊就要驅散。"},{"pid":"bf94dfec66a59934579a4542218722aa23fdff5c","tid":1947484,"uid":117722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"181804f65b968f6dff91a0377dd1e868bb868546","tid":1947484,"uid":267801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:06:57.000Z","msg":"dklm 香港地有邊度唔使排隊，係唔係一排隊就要驅散。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T09:17:28.000Z","msg":"條街有冇咁闊"}]}